{"tid":556470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人係點諗 求小醒","createTime":"2018-02-10T13:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T07:43:31.000Z","uid":140656,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d337bc655bc9af578c6f7142fcf129171572f9fe","tid":556470,"uid":140656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:25:59.000Z","msg":"一齊左一段時間了 一開頭都秒回 叫曬老婆<br />\n之後就話未投入到（咁又叫老婆 咩心態？）但係又會做親密既行為 <br />\n愈來愈無野傾 話訓教但又WhatsApp FB 又online <br />\n係咪騎牛搵馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來好少關心我 問我既野 <br />\n對朋友就好多野講 對我就好靜 <br />\n無咩熱戀甜蜜既感覺 <br />\n次次都係我問出街 出親街定時送我搭車 自己番屋企<br />\n唔係應該會想留得幾耐就幾耐既咩 <br />\n又話想日日痴實我 都假既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始都咁樣 之後點算<br />\n港女啲咁講  佢係朋友身上用幾多錢都得 食放題去AIA<br />\n同我一齊睇場戲都話貴 食左幾次麥當勞譚仔（我地AA)<br />\n成日暗示我 佢好窮 我都無叫過你買野俾我...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求小醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔愛我就放開我喇 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508bb87fbd4e931822f458236b92ad4a8cbe521e","tid":556470,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"一齊多久了？<br />\n會不會是淡了"},{"pid":"a1d492a15039dfab54d48f2e415c18ecddd0acc9","tid":556470,"uid":78622,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚窮寒"},{"pid":"8c59a71df52da6a0b4cca19ebbd60f028a27d56d","tid":556470,"uid":157420,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:29:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">冇</span>事嘅<br />\n留低tg <br />\n我慰藉下你"},{"pid":"f4e4e9ee60c2bc40101ef375191bbe44b069eb5f","tid":556470,"uid":61653,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"做咗咁撚耐男人都唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22afb75d2e9a71831b42018c313f45227abb11f","tid":556470,"uid":140656